snippet.title: Rune Factory 5 - Gameplay Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Build a new life amidst a grand adventure in the heartwarming RPG, Rune Factory 5! Protect your town as a peacekeeping ranger, harvest crops, go fishing, and find romance! Your new life in a fantasy world begins in 2021.

Learn More: https://nintendo.com/games/detail/rune-factory-5-switch/
